          "reviewBody": "I have no complaint regarding the educational aspect of this school.\nBut this is a complaint from a citizen who is fed up with this school’s parking facility which creates a daily chaos for general public  travelling for their day to day work.\nI don’t know if they have a school bus or any such facility but what all I see is numerous cars daily coming to pick up n number of students which blocks the road and hinders the daily travelers.\nI would really want the concerned authorities to look into this matter and take the action required ASAP .",
